snippet.title: First Salary Day after Demonetisation, Big Test for Modi Government

localized.description:
Today is the first salary day after demonetisation. It is the big test for Modi government in first week of December. ATMs and banks are running out of cash since demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000. RBI assures that there is enough cash and more than 210 tons of cash has been transferred to RBI branches across the country.
